  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistancesMap<P extends XYPosition,T extends RawData>
    Given a ( (x,y) , value ) fingerprint map, the instance of a DistancesMap represents the collection of pairs ( (x,y) , distance ) where distances refer to the last observed measurement.
    FingerprintMap<P extends XYPosition,T extends RawData>
    An object representing a generic fingerprint map with some utility methods.
    FingerprintMapBuilder<F extends FingerprintMap>
    A factory class for FingerprintMap objects.
    MagneticFingerprintMap
    FingerprintMap subtype for Magnetic Fingerprints.
    MagneticFingerprintMap.Builder
    Builder class for MagneticFingerprintMap.
    PositionDistance<P extends XYPosition>
    Wrapper class for (position,distance) pairs.
    WifiFingerprintMap
    FingerprintMap subtype for Wifi Fingerprints.
    WifiFingerprintMap.Builder
    Builder class for WifiFingerprintMap.
